raw_data.sellerName: OCEAN LIFE INSURANCE PUBLIC COMPANY LIMITED
raw_data.releaseNotes:
The OCEAN CLUB APP offers a variety of features to help individuals plan their health effectively because everyone's health is different! 

This app will help you understand your health better and make tracking your health data enjoyable, all while working towards your goals and even having the chance to earn rewards for your commitment to improving your health. 

Here are some of the features provided by the OCEAN CLUB APP: 

Nutrition Tracker: 
      - Customize plans tailored to each individual's health goals, serving as a guide for meal planning by selecting recommended plans based on the user's health objectives. 
      - Track your food intake to gain better self-awareness. Monitor calorie intake and nutrition details such as protein, carbohydrates, and fat to plan appropriate diet and exercise routines. 

Exercise Tracker: 
      - Utilize another tool developed by the OCEAN CLUB APP to manage your health by seamlessly syncing health data from Smart Watches such as Google Fit, Garmin Connect, and Apple Health. 
      - Enjoy the freedom to walk, run, or cycle at your convenience without needing to carry your mobile phone all the time. Earn OCHI COIN daily by successfully completing fitness missions. 

Relax Tracker:  
      - Keep track of your sleep patterns, stress levels, and heart rate by extracting data from wearable devices. 
      - Receive notifications if your heart rate is abnormal, allowing you to promptly respond to any irregularities. 

The OCEAN CLUB APP will introduce many more health-related features soon to help you become a better version of yourself. Stay tuned!

Ocean Club Application พัฒนากิจกรรมเพื่อสุขภาพ (Health Function) เพื่อช่วยให้สมาชิกสนุกกับการใส่ใจเรื่องสุขภาพของตัวเอง เพื่อนำไปสู่การมีสุขภาพที่ดีขึ้นกว่าเดิม ด้วยกิจกรรมทั้ง 4 ได้แก่ เดิน วิ่ง ปั่นจักรยาน และนอน โดยเชื่อมต่อข้อมูลกับฟรีแอปพลิเคชัน (เช่น Apple Health แอปพลิเคชัน) ให้สมาชิกสนุกกับการสะสม OCHI COIN (เหรียญโอชิ) ได้ทุกครั้งที่ออกกำลังกาย

Everyone can easily access top class privileges and exclusive activities. Enjoy the app by collecting points (Ochi Coin) to redeem special deals and offers from more than 250 Ocean Club Partners through “Shop-Chim-Chill” activities nationwide. Moreover, be able to access our online services which will help facilitate our members more easily with their policy information, networked hospital and much more. 
Ocean Club Application developed health functions that enable Ocean Club App users track their health activities in order to enhance health quality; i.e. walking, running, cycling, and sleeping by integrating with free application such as Apple Health App. Not a customer? Just download our app to explore more.

apps.title: Inner Circle: Dating Community
apps.description:
Inner Circle is a curated members community for people who live ambitious, interesting lifestyles – and want to date people who move in the same circles. 

Built on the belief that opposites don’t attract, everything starts with two important questions: What are you interested in? And where do you spend your time? 

Our community is niche by design, and not everyone will be accepted. Each application is reviewed by our membership team to curate a community of people with shared lifestyles and who move in the same circles. 

Once approved, you'll be a guest in the community and can earn access to features like messaging by inviting friends. Alternatively, you have the opportunity to become an Inner Circle member through a paid subscription. As a member you’re part of something bigger, with full use of the app to connect with the community, as well as invites to events. 

You’re not for everyone, 
you’re for someone. 


--- T&Cs ---
Inner Circle is a subscription-based app and members who want to access all the features, or set different preferences, can subscribe for a membership.
The membership price is clearly displayed within the app. We offer weekly and monthly subscriptions, plus 3-month and 6-month deals giving discounts on the monthly price.
Please note that the price may vary per country, and is subject to change without notice.
Inner Circle is free to download and limited features can be used without a subscription.
Payment will be charged to your iTunes account. Your subscription will automatically renew, unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can switch off auto-renewal at any time after purchase by going to your settings in the iTunes Store. If you choose not to subscribe for a membership, you can simply continue using and enjoying Inner Circle for free. 
Be sure to read our Privacy Policy and Terms and Conditions: 
https://www.theinnercircle.co/privacy 
https://www.theinnercircle.co/tos

apps.title: Feeld: Open-Minded Dating App
apps.description:
Feeld was made for you to connect with open-minded people looking to explore dating and relationships in a safe and private way. Chat & connect on an alternative dating app created for anyone and everyone. Feeld is open to anyone looking for an exciting, new type of dating experience.

Discover a space to be your true self and let the people looking for you find you. Join Feeld to explore virtual or other locations and connect with like-minded individuals worldwide. Connect openly in a diverse community open to all genders and sexual identities as you redefine your relationships to self and others on Feeld.

Discover an open-minded dating experience when you download today.


FEELD FEATURES

CHAT & CONNECT
• Meet open-minded humans and start up a conversation
• Connect with people closest to you, or explore 20+ of our most popular cities around the world
• Find people looking to connect and discover a new way to date

A DATING APP MADE FOR EVERYONE
• Choose from over 20 gender identities
• Pick from a list of 20+ sexualities to personalize your Feeld experience

DATE YOUR WAY
• Explore safely on a secure and private dating platform
• Connect with curious Feeld members and explore your desires
• Chat with open-minded Feeld members for meaningful, intimate experiences

As seen in: New York Times, The New Yorker, Dazed & Confused, Cosmopolitan and Vanity Fair.

Become Majestic for the full Feeld experience. With a Majestic membership, you can enjoy enhanced features such as seeing who liked you on the app, adding private photos visible only to your Connections, one free Ping a day, and more.

Download Feeld, a place to explore curiosity and desires, and date in a different way. Connect with other people around the world that are ready for a new, exciting way to date.

______

You must be at least 18 years of age to access and use Feeld.

The app is free to download and use.

Additional features are available when you join the Majestic Membership, an optional paid subscription service that funds the app’s development.

Subscriptions must be managed by the members and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the App Store Subscriptions screen after purchase. 

When a trial subscription is offered, the trial period begins when a member signs up for the subscription through their App Store account. The subscription will be charged on the last day of the trial unless the member cancels at least 24 hours before trial ends.

Any unused portion of a free trial period will be forfeited when the member purchases a subscription.

To cancel the Membership, members must cancel directly through their App Store account.

Cancellations begin at the end of the current subscription period.

All purchases are billed to the payment method that you designate when you sign up for an Apple ID as part of your App Store account and will appear as Apple on your App Store statement.

All personal data is handled under the Terms of Use of Feeld Privacy Policy. More details can be found here: https://feeld.co/about/privacy.

Terms of Use can be found here: https://feeld.co/about/terms

raw_data.releaseNotes: Good connections need a strong foundation. This update keeps things solid with small fixes and steady improvements.

apps.title: Hani: Your Lifestyle Assistant
apps.description:
Hani is your go-to assistant and search companion for exploring Paris. It guarantees recommendations for places that align with your preferred ambiance and lifestyle, curated by our team of experts.

Using Hani makes navigating the city simple, with a streamlined four-step process to discover spots for dining, getting a drink, enjoying a coffee, exploring art galleries, shopping, and dancing. You can experience all of this with your chosen company, at your convenience, in the atmosphere you prefer, and in line with your lifestyle.

With Hani, you have the freedom to be yourself, enjoy the vibe you want, share moments with anyone you choose, whenever you like, and make the most of each experience.

Introducing Hani: Your Ultimate City Explorer!

Discovering the best the city has to offer with Hani – the app designed for simplicity and tailored experiences. In just 4 easy steps, unlock a personalized list of recommendations based on:

Lifestyle Preferences:
Choose between creative, alternative, hedonistic, shaping your Parisian experience according to the lifestyle you desire.

Activity Selection:
Whether you're in the mood to eat, drink, enjoy coffee, explore culture, shop, or dance the night away, Hani has you covered with curated suggestions.

Social Settings:
Specify your company preferences – whether solo, on a date, or in a group – ensuring your Paris adventure suits your social vibe.

Ambiance Desires:
Tailor your experience further by selecting the ambiance that suits you best – be it design, casual, chic, or a variety of other atmospheres.

advisories: Frequent/Intense Alcohol, Tobacco, or Drug Use or References

apps.title: IN9 Lifestyle
apps.description:
IN9 is the next-generation members club.

As high performers ourselves, we understand first-hand the importance of life-work balance. Through experience, we know that managing leisure alongside a hectic schedule can be a daunting task. That’s why we have invested our knowledge, connections, and expertise to create a comprehensive lifestyle system tailored for high performers like us. 

We are dedicated to offering our members services exclusively from partners we know and trust. Along with our talented team, we personally choose, test, and share information about the finest events, experiences and services we have personally used, ensuring that our recommendations are genuine, vetted, and reliable. We care for our clients as we would for our friends, providing them with the best terms and prices through our personal connections and experiences.

Constantly on the lookout for new and exciting recommendations, we are committed to sharing only the best with our members. We believe in transparency and showcasing only what truly deserves your precious time. We invite you to join us and discover a new standard of leisure management curated by people who understand and share a high-achieving, dynamic lifestyle.

apps.title: Acilect - Personal App
apps.description:
This innovative app is ideal for those who desire the simplicity of managing their lifestyle interests, needs, and activities all from one easy source.

Acilect provides direct channels for individuals to manage their interests efficiently without having to install several apps to perform different tasks or demands at any time or place. 

With its impressive list of innovative features and standard quality delivery process, you’ll no longer have to juggle the capabilities of separate apps to perform at the same level of efficiency that acilect offers from one single source.

Through the power of one seamless app, users are able to engage with any business or organization on demand.

Acilect provides incomparable flexibility for users to customize features that support their specific lifestyle needs or interests, which helps you accomplish your scheduled or day-to-day interests effortlessly. 

Designed to help individuals access opportunities and achieve great value by focusing exclusively on unique interests and effectively improving every process. 
And the best part is that it can be done anytime, anywhere, with just a few simple clicks. And all with the seamless, user-friendly, and intuitive features of acilect.

It’s flexible. It’s efficient. It’s convenient and reliable. And it’s the way of the future.

This app is available for individual users (personal). If you have other acilect accounts, please use the app provided for such accounts or check the website at www.acilect.com for more details.

What if the only way to use a social app…was to actually be social?

First Round’s On Me (FROM) is an approval-only social app that rewards you for making plans, and showing up. It’s for the friends escaping the endless group chats, the coworkers who need an excuse to leave Slack, for the couples remembering why date night matters. Just a drink, time and place with your people at our curated list of New York City’s top bars, restaurants and cafés.

[ FIND YOUR PEOPLE ]
• Add the friends you want to catch up with, or discover new connections near you. 

[ CONNECTION SHOULDN'T BE COMPLICATED ]
•  Sync your calendar, see when your people are free, and share your availability all in one place.

[ MAKE A PLAN IN SECONDS ]
• Pick a Drink, Time & Place, then send the invite—done.

[ GET REWARDED FOR SHOWING UP ]
• Receive & redeem drink credits.

[ QUALITY VENUES FOR QUALITY MEMBERS ]
•  Redeem those drink credits at our curated list of New York City’s top bars, restaurants and cafés. Enjoy a round on us with a two-drink minimum

[ SAFETY YOU CAN TRUST ]
• Referral and waitlist only membership that fosters a community-first culture.

[ UPGRADE FOR EVEN BETTER CONNECTION ]
• Everything in our Classic membership, plus 50 credits each month, access to The Social Club in Chelsea, a complimentary coffee every day, guest passes & plus-one privileges, along with free entry to all events.

[ A COMMUNITY BEYOND THE APP ]
• A Members club in the heart of Manhattan, city guides, and curated events—because we know that real community lives offline.

▶ WHAT OTHERS ARE SAYING ◀

”In an industry that relies on the steady demand for human connection, FROM is emerging as a strong new player.” - LA Times

“Their physical space dovetails with the app’s design, perfect for in-person connection.” - NY Post

“An app is inspired by a time when people met organically.” – Yahoo.com

 “A movement in the human connection space” - Pulse 2.0

You have no more excuses not to get that drink. We make it easy to plan, meet, and connect in real life—with the people who matter. Download First Round’s On Me (F.R.O.M) today.

apps.title: Transliving Magazine
apps.description:
Transliving International is the magazine that amplifies the voice of all Gender Diverse and Trans people. It doesn't matter whether you think of yourself as MtF, FtM, Non-Binary (NB), Gender Fluid, TS, TG or TV or CD, or something else, or simply "me". Transliving is published for and welcomes everyone on the transgender (Trans) spectrum.

Each quarter, Transliving magazine delivers you 100 full-colour pages featuring interviews and high-quality photo shoots. You’ll also find plenty of articles to keep you up-to-date on issues affecting the gender diverse and trans community with hard-hitting comment and opinion. Along with features covering real-life stories, event reports & listings, readers' contacts, fashion, make-up & beauty features, partners' & family features. Information, support & advice and so much more...

Join the community with a subscription to Transliving magazine today - a must-read for all Gender Diverse / Trans people worldwide! 

----------------------------------------------

This is a free app download. Within the app users can purchase the current issue and back issues.

Subscriptions are also available within the application. A subscription will start from the latest regular issue at the time of purchase.

-The subscription will renew automatically unless cancelled more than 24 hours before the end of the current period. You will be charged for renewal within 24 hours of the end of the current period, for the same duration and at the current subscription rate for the product.
-You may turn off the auto-renewal of subscriptions through your Account Settings, however you are not able to cancel the current subscription during its active period.
-Payment will be charged to your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase and any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when a subscription to that publication is purchased.
-If a subscription offers a free trial, at the end of the trial period, you will be charged the full price of the subscription. You may cancel a subscription during its free trial period via the subscription settings on your iTunes account. This must be done 24 hours before the end of the subscription period to avoid being charged.

Users can register for/ login to a pocketmags account in-app. This will protect their issues in the case of a lost device and allow browsing of purchases on multiple platforms. Existing pocketmags users can retrieve their purchases by logging into their account.

We recommend loading the app for the first time in a wi-fi area so that all issue data is retrieved.
If your app will not load past the splash page after a first install or an update, please delete and reinstall the app from the App Store

Help and frequently asked questions can be accessed in-app and on pocketmags.

If you have any problems at all please do not hesitate to contact us: help@pocketmags.com

--------------------

http://www.pocketmags.com/privacy.aspx

apps.title: Paired: Couples & Relationship
apps.description:
Welcome to Paired: the app that brings couples closer. Life can be messy, but your relationship doesn’t have to be. Paired helps you build better communication, manage conflict, and deepen your connection in just 5 minutes a day.

- 8 million downloads
- Apple App of the Day, January 2024
- Scientifically proven to increase relationship satisfaction
- Featured in The New York Times, BBC News, Bustle, and more

With Paired, you can:

- Make connection a daily habit: Daily questions allow you to effortlessly dedicate time each day to build strong communication, encourage intimacy, and strengthen your relationship.
- Pair with your partner: Add your answers and then unlock your partners responses to start a discussion, discover more about them and build a deep connection. 
- Celebrate every event, big or small: Use Paired to keep track of the important dates in your relationship, from the big ones like anniversaries and birthdays, to the small, significant moments, like your first kiss or your favorite date night.

With Paired Premium, you can:

- Reach your relationship goals: Our guided journeys support you in developing the skills you need to help your relationship to thrive, with activities and conversations each day to help you build healthy communication habits. 
- Focus on the topics that matter: Dive into any topic, from household finances to love languages, with guidance from experts to ensure sure it’s always healthy and productive.
- Check in with each other: Our games and quizzes are suitable for all stages of your relationship, whether you’re married, newly dating, or in a long-distance relationship. 

Join millions around the world using the Paired, the app for couples, to build happier, lasting relationships.

Questions? Suggestions? Let us know at support@paired.com.

*****

Please note that Paired and the materials and information contained herein are not intended to, and do not constitute medical, psychological, or mental health advice, or diagnosis, and may not be used for such purposes. You should always consult with a qualified physician or mental health professional about your specific circumstances.

Our Privacy Policy: https://www.paired.com/privacy_policy.html
Our Terms and Conditions: https://www.paired.com/terms_and_conditions.html

apps.title: Sweat: Fitness App For Women
apps.developer: The Bikini Body Training Company Pty Ltd
apps.description:
Train at home or in the gym with one of the world’s largest women’s fitness communities! Get the fitness motivation you need with Sweat, a personal training app featuring co-founder and elite head trainer, Kayla Itsines. 

Sweat offers a broad suite of challenging, yet achievable programs with workouts you can do anywhere, anytime to progressively build your fitness. New programs give you more ways to push yourself and get you closer to reaching your goals. Stay accountable with virtual community challenges and feel supported by like-minded women everywhere.

Join Kayla and Sweat’s other world-class trainers: Kelsey Wells, Britany Williams, Cass Olholm — and more! — on your journey to discovering fitness confidence.

All new members get exclusive access to a free trial.

Find a training style you enjoy with easy-to-follow beginner, intermediate and advanced workouts, including:
- HIIT (High-intensity interval training)
- Circuit Training
- Bodyweight exercises
- Powerbuilding
- Strength training
- Yoga
- Barre
- Pilates
- Recovery
- Cardio
- Pregnancy and postnatal

Train your way — follow a program or work out on demand. Choose workouts that suit your lifestyle with no equipment, free weights or machines and express workouts when you are short on time. 

Sweat’s features make it simple to stay on track and keep on top of your progress. Features include:
- Exercise descriptions and video demonstrations
- Exercise substitutions to make movements harder or easier
- Trainer audio cues
- Log weights used during gym-based programs
- Planner to schedule your workouts and track your weekly progress
- Share “sweaty selfies” with your friends and the Sweat Community to keep motivated
- Comprehensive education section covering fitness, nutrition and wellbeing
- Over 200 fresh & fast meals for every lifestyle
- Daily step and hydration trackers
- 24/7 access to the Sweat Community

Enable Apple Health with your Apple Watch to keep track of all your activity in the Sweat app.

SUBSCRIPTION PRICING & TERMS
Sweat is free to download. Ongoing use requires an active subscription, available on a monthly or yearly basis. New customers who choose a monthly subscription are eligible for a free trial period. Yearly subscriptions are billed the total annual fee from purchase date. Monthly subscription users are billed per month.

Payment will be charged to your credit card through your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase. Subscription renews automatically unless cancelled at least 24 hours prior to the end of the subscription period. There is no increase in price when renewing.

Subscriptions can be managed and auto-renewal turned off in Account Settings in iTunes after purchase. Once purchased, refunds will not be provided for any unused portion of the term. Read our full Terms and conditions & Privacy Policy:
https://www.sweat.com/pages/terms-and-conditions
https://www.sweat.com/privacy

apps.description:
With hundreds of mindfulness meditation apps to pick from, what makes Meditopia so special? Well, unlike most of the other options, Meditopia offers more than just a short-term solution to falling asleep, finding balance and de-stressing; we offer each member over 1000 deep-dive meditations and breathing exercises that get right to the heart of what we as a people, regardless of age, background, or experience, are dealing with everyday.

These meditations, offered in 12 languages, aim to cover the entire spectrum of human experiences from relationships, expectations, acceptance, and loneliness, to our body-image, sexuality, life purpose, and feelings of inadequacy. Meditopia doesn’t just want to be a band-aid for wounds which we know require permanent healing. Our goal is to create a mental health sanctuary in which you can access the guidance and tools you need to build up mental resilience, calm, balance, a healthy headspace and peace of mind. Everything you need to feel happier, relax, and sleep like a baby.

Download now and try a free meditation! 

What can you get with Meditopia?

Sleep Meditations + Breathing exercises
Your quality of sleep affects almost every aspect of your daily life. So why not help yourself get better sleep? Try any one of our +30 sleep meditations to learn new techniques as well as breathing and visualization exercises that you can continue to practice throughout the rest of your life to promote good sleep. Say bye to that old sound machine and that one-function breathing app.

Bedtime Stories 
Bedtime fairy stories aren’t just for kids! As you tuck yourself into bed, all warm and cozy, let us lull you to sleep with our wide selection of bedtime stories. From fairy tales and adventures to experiences in places all throughout the world, feel yourself getting pulled into these vivid and soothing stories. After all, at the end of a long day, you deserve to gently ease into a dreamworld of sleep and recovery. We also have a wide library of sleep sounds like rain, waves, and relaxing noises like white noise and more.

AI Therapy
Introducing SOUL, our custom AI therapy solution. Designed by psychologists and mental health experts, SOUL is your AI mental health companion. Tailored to address diverse mental health needs, SOUL utilizes its intricate understanding of language nuances to offer personalized support, engaging users in insightful and compassionate dialogue

Apple Watch + Siri Shortcuts
Even if you don't have your iPhone with you, you can access all of our content from Apple Watch!

Our Top Features:
+1000 guided meditations
Nature sounds with a timer
Independent WatchOS app
Apple HealthKit integration to count your worry-free minutes
Dark Mode support
Daily Meditations on a new topic every day
Daily Inspirational Quotes
Personal Note-taking to track your progress
Mindful Meter to see your mindfulness stats at a glance
In-app challenges with friends to feel challenged
Custom reminders to sleep and meditate

User-friendly and user-oriented interface

Meditopia doesn’t just want to be a band-aid for wounds which we know require permanent healing. Our goal is to create a mental health sanctuary in which you can access the guidance and tools you need to build up mental resilience, calm, balance, a healthy headspace and peace of mind. Everything you need to feel happier, relax, and sleep like a baby.

Download now and try a free meditation! 

What can you get with Meditopia?

Sleep Meditations + Breathing exercises
Your quality of sleep affects almost every aspect of your daily life. So why not help yourself get better sleep? Try any one of our +30 sleep meditations to learn new techniques as well as breathing and visualization exercises that you can continue to practice throughout the rest of your life to promote good sleep. Say bye to that old sound machine and that one-function breathing app.

Bedtime Stories 
Bedtime fairy stories aren’t just for kids! As you tuck yourself into bed, all warm and cozy, let us lull you to sleep with our wide selection of bedtime stories. From fairy tales and adventures to experiences in places all throughout the world, feel yourself getting pulled into these vivid and soothing stories. After all, at the end of a long day, you deserve to gently ease into a dreamworld of sleep and recovery. We also have a wide library of sleep sounds like rain, waves, and relaxing noises like white noise and more.

AI Therapy
Introducing SOUL, our custom AI therapy solution. Designed by psychologists and mental health experts, SOUL is your AI mental health companion. Tailored to address diverse mental health needs, SOUL utilizes its intricate understanding of language nuances to offer personalized support, engaging users in insightful and compassionate dialogue

Apple Watch + Siri Shortcuts
Even if you don't have your iPhone with you, you can access all of our content from Apple Watch!

+1000 guided meditations
Nature sounds with a timer
Independent WatchOS app
Apple HealthKit integration to count your worry-free minutes
Dark Mode support
Daily Meditations on a new topic every day
Daily Inspirational Quotes

In-app challenges with friends to feel challenged
Custom reminders to sleep and meditate

User-friendly and user-oriented interface

apps.title: Grailed – Buy & Sell Fashion
apps.description:
Buy, Sell, Discover. Join Grailed, a trusted platform for personal style, and connect with a global community of over 10M+ style enthusiasts. Explore curated collections featuring millions of menswear and womenswear pieces from 10K+ designers. Whether you're looking to buy coveted pieces, sell pre-loved items from your closet, or discover the latest trends, you can do it with confidence on Grailed.

BUY, SELL & ROTATE YOUR WARDROBE
Experience trusted and protected transactions on a platform designed for the style-savvy. With low seller fees and direct exposure to a hub of buyers, it's time to rotate your wardrobe and profit from your style.

SHOP THE LATEST TRENDS
Shop with confidence with Grailed’s authentication practices and purchase protection for qualified transactions. Unlock great prices and negotiate with sellers for deals. Explore menswear and womenswear styles for any aesthetic across apparel, footwear, accessories and more.
• Vintage: Designer, Denim, Band Tees, Leather Jackets, Y2K-inspired styles
• Luxury: Gucci, Dior, Prada, Chanel, Louis Vuitton, Rolex
• Streetwear: Off-White, Supreme, Nike, Jordan, adidas, New Balance
• Avant-Garde: Raf Simons, Rick Owens, Maison Margiela, Comme des Garçons, Helmut Lang

READ REVIEWS FROM THE COMMUNITY
Seller Ratings, Reviews, Transaction History and Seller Badges provide transparency and added peace of mind. Grailed relies on direct feedback from community members to provide additional accountability.

ENJOY A PERSONALIZED EXPERIENCE
The Grailed feed serves personalized recommendations tailored to your style. Follow designers and sellers, receive notifications for saved searches and price drops, and filter your feed to match your preferences. Explore curated collections and dive into our 'Trending' and 'For You' selects designed with your style in mind.

DISCOVER AND GET INSPIRED
Get style inspiration through editorial content like street style and designer deep dives. Whether you're evolving your personal style, exploring new trends, or looking for the perfect piece to complete your wardrobe, Grailed is your one-stop-shop.

GRAILED IN THE NEWS
Grailed has been featured across accredited publications, including Vogue, The New York Times Style, Harper’s Bazaar, GQ, Esquire, Bloomberg, Nylon, WWD, Dazed, Elle, WhoWhatWear, Highsnobiety, Complex, Hypebeast and more.

随时随地预订酒店、机票、火车票、汽车票、景点门票、用车，跟团游、周末游、自由行、自驾游、邮轮、旅游度假等产品！畅享旅游攻略；出行、旅游不用愁！

apps.title: Mindbody: Fitness & Wellness
apps.description:
Mindbody is the world’s #1 booking platform for fitness, beauty, and wellness experiences. We encourage people to try new things and find what makes them feel physically, mentally, and spiritually their best.  
Whether it’s a class, salon service, or meditation session, we’ve got options.  
 
With over 40k+ studios around the world, we offer top fitness classes like yoga, Pilates, barre, dance, HIIT, bootcamp, and more. Looking for something along the lines of a massage, hair treatment, or cryotherapy? We’ve got that too. Plus, you’ll find promoted intro offers and last-minute deals—it’s all on the app. 
 
How it works: 
* Download the free app, then create a Mindbody account (or log in to your existing account) to get started. 
* Enter your location at the top of the screen to see local intro offers, price drops, and deals near you.  
* Looking for something in particular? Jump to the “SEARCH” icon at the bottom of the window to find businesses near you. From there, you can type in the desired service or browse popular categories. 
* Need to refine your results? Filter your search by business, class, date, time, distance, or category. You can also sort based on what’s recommended, top-rated or closest to you. 
* Once you select a class or appointment, you can read up on reviews, instructor & service provider bios, and how to get there. You can also choose a business first to learn more about their amenities, schedule, services, location, and pricing. 
* When you’re ready to secure your service, select the “Book” button in the right-hand corner. From there, you will be asked to confirm your payment information. Plug in your info, then hit “BOOK AND BUY” to make it official.

apps.title: Pacaso
apps.description:
Pacaso is the leading co-ownership marketplace for buying, owning and selling a luxury vacation home. We offer fully managed LLC co-ownership, with professional home management and a smart scheduling system to make owning more accessible and hassle-free — you simply show up and relax. We’ve curated the best listings so you can find the right vacation home that brings everyone together.

With the Pacaso app, you can shop from fully furnished, luxury Pacaso homes ready for immediate ownership, or explore third-party listings in your favorite community. Listings with the most buyer interest will be turned into Pacaso homes.

Once you become an owner, you can manage your home in the Pacaso app. The SmartStay™ scheduling system makes booking time easy and equitable for owners based on the number of shares owned. Owners can also track operating expenses, see how many stays they have available, refer friends and contact their home's property management team through the app.

apps.title: Zoosk - Social Dating App
apps.description:
Match, Chat, Date

Rediscover the fun of dating with Zoosk. Find like-minded singles and make more meaningful connections with features such as SmartPicks which uses behavioral matchmaking, the Carousel which helps you find new people, and our live streaming feature available 24/7. Search, chat, date - the opportunities are endless on Zoosk. Download the app for free today and start making more meaningful social interactions with other singles.

The Zoosk Difference

- Free live-streaming feature, Zoosk Live, available 24/7
- Search and browse profiles, find online singles and connect in real-time
- Customize your search experience based on your preferences
- Start new connections by sending positive interactions such as smiles and likes
- Use Carousel to discover new people by responding with a yes or no

Zoosk Subscriber* Advantages:

- Set filters for specific options such as religion, children, education, smoking, and more
- Chat with your connections
- Unlock and connect with people who've viewed you
- Say yes to and start chatting with your SmartPicks™ for matches based on compatibility

Exclusive features*:

- Boost your profile for more visibility and attract more attention from other members
- Get Delivery Confirmation on messages
- Premium messaging lets you receive messages from all singles

We Prioritize Safe Dating

While our goal is to make dating enjoyable and help people connect, we take safety seriously. Our Photo Verification tool gives you confidence that the person you’re talking to looks like their profile picture. And with 40 million members, we are one of the most trusted and loved dating apps. With Zoosk you can focus on finding the love of your life without worry.

Why People Love Zoosk

"The dating service has made it really easy to start a profile, meet other users, and cast a wide net for potential matches." - Mashable
"Launched in 2007, Zoosk has become the toast of the online dating world" - AskMen

About Zoosk

Zoosk is an inclusive and welcoming community that celebrates diversity and encourages people to be their authentic selves. We believe everyone deserves love and are committed to creating a safe and supportive environment for our singles. We leverage technology to help single meet friendly people and feel supported every step of their journey. We are one of the best dating apps for meeting someone searching for love online. No more unfulfilling searches: download Zoosk and get ready because meeting someone is just a click away.

---------------------------------------------------------------------

*ADDITIONAL COSTS AND AUTO RENEW:

All subscriptions and upgrades like coins (including subscription upgrades and upgrades without a subscription) automatically renew at the end of the term for the same duration and you will be charged again for the same amount (plus any applicable taxes) unless you cancel by turning off auto-renewal at least 24 hours before the end of their term.

Turn off the auto-renewal through your account settings. Once you turn off auto-renewal, your subscription and/or upgrades will expire at the end of their term. To learn more, see Terms of Use

Agreement at http://www.zoosk.com/tos and our FAQs at http://zoosk.com/help. Also, read our Privacy Policy at www.zoosk.com/privacy and online dating safety guide at https://www.zoosk.com/safety.

Prices are in U.S. dollars, exclude any applicable sales tax, may vary in countries other than the U.S., and are subject to change without notice.

---------------------------------------------------------------------

> Date Mix: https://www.zoosk.com/date-mix/

apps.title: Park Home & Holiday Living
apps.description:
Are you looking to escape the pressures and responsibilities of running a large house now that the kids have flown the nest? Perhaps your pension may not have achieved your expectations, then a park home could offer a perfect solution!

The UK’s only consumer magazine potential residents, residents, park site owners, home manufacturers or associated service providers.

There are an estimated 180,000 park homeowners throughout the UK, with most living on privately owned sites.

Residents highlight the benefits of living in a park home, namely the low maintenance of the property, the community spirit, proximity to amenities and the minimal hassle.

Readers can expect: profiles of the UK’s most exciting parks; new model home reviews; expert legal help; top buying advice; specialist suppliers and services; industry news; updates of important shows and events; small gardens; DIY and home improvements; and a comprehensive new holiday section!

Park Home & Holiday Living also produces definitive annuals including Residential Parks Guide and The Ultimate Lodge Guide. 

----------------------------------------------

This is a free app download. Within the app users can purchase the current issue and back issues.

Subscriptions are also available within the application. A subscription will start from the latest regular issue at the time of purchase.

-The subscription will renew automatically unless cancelled more than 24 hours before the end of the current period. You will be charged for renewal within 24 hours of the end of the current period, for the same duration and at the current subscription rate for the product.
-You may turn off the auto-renewal of subscriptions through your Account Settings, however you are not able to cancel the current subscription during its active period.
-Payment will be charged to your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase and any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when a subscription to that publication is purchased.
-If a subscription offers a free trial, at the end of the trial period, you will be charged the full price of the subscription. You may cancel a subscription during its free trial period via the subscription settings on your iTunes account. This must be done 24 hours before the end of the subscription period to avoid being charged.

Users can register for/ login to a pocketmags account in-app. This will protect their issues in the case of a lost device and allow browsing of purchases on multiple platforms. Existing pocketmags users can retrieve their purchases by logging into their account.

We recommend loading the app for the first time in a wi-fi area so that all issue data is retrieved.
If your app will not load past the splash page after a first install or an update, please delete and reinstall the app from the App Store

Help and frequently asked questions can be accessed in-app and on pocketmags.

If you have any problems at all please do not hesitate to contact us: help@pocketmags.com

--------------------

You can find our privacy policy here:
http://www.pocketmags.com/privacy.aspx

You can find our terms and conditions here:
http://www.pocketmags.com/terms.aspx

We always love to hear from you - please don’t hesitate to contact us at info@pocketmags.com with any feedback or if you require assistance
